---
name: Choice
notes: |
  Choice modals pose a question to the user.
order: 1
previewClass: drizzle-u-bgBlack35 drizzle-u-drizzleModalOverride
---
<div
  class="sprk-c-Modal sprk-u-Hide"
  role="dialog" tabindex="-1"
  aria-labelledby="modal-choice-heading"
  aria-modal="true"
  aria-describedby="modal-content-id-1"
  data-sprk-modal="choice">
  <header class="sprk-c-Modal__header">
    <h2 class="sprk-b-TypeDisplayThree" id="modal-choice-heading">
      Are you sure?
    </h2>
  </header>

  <div class="sprk-c-Modal__body">
    <p class="sprk-b-TypeBodyTwo">
      This is some content that is in a modal. It explains what the modal is for.
      There will also be a way to close the modal.
    </p>
  </div>

  <footer class="sprk-c-Modal__footer">
    <button class="sprk-c-Button">
      Confirm
    </button>

    <a class="sprk-b-Link sprk-b-Link--standalone" href="" data-sprk-modal-cancel="choice">
      Cancel
    </a>
  </footer>
</div>
<div data-sprk-modal="choice" class="sprk-c-ModalMask sprk-u-Hide"></div>
